'''Amsel''' was the site of the [[Galactic Senate/Legends|Senate]] of [[Aquilae (The Star Wars)|Aquilae]]. [[King/Legends|King]] [[Kayos]] left the [[Palace of Lite]] to oppose the proposed treaty with the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. He was ambushed and killed en route, and the Senate surrendered.

